{"tid":243553,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救)隻貓壓住我隻手訓左，點算?","createTime":"2017-05-14T17:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T18:43:45.000Z","uid":10111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81ee5b3261ad9688cb11762b0a4bf6ba1fbdd1dc","tid":243553,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:29:55.000Z","msg":"話說隻貓病左，我係隔離post <br />\n問緊咁多位巴絲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 既時候<br />\n(有無熟貓既朋友)隻貓今日嘔左七次<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/243462/page/2?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/243462/page/2?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n佢就靠住我隻手訓左<br />\n一開始係咁訓<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/012524_1b84926f7fd7b3e24cec32352840a26e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F012524_1b84926f7fd7b3e24cec32352840a26e.jpg&h=095e684f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後佢無啦啦起左身，我以為佢唔舒服摸下佢啦<br />\n點知佢就壓住我隻手訓左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身念住等一陣，但佢壓左成五分鐘都未郁<br />\n依家feel隻手開始出汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴絲建議下點攞番隻手出黎，又唔嘈醒佢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/012815_26c433d4cd8e7e5753c66bf677cb745c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F012815_26c433d4cd8e7e5753c66bf677cb745c.jpg&h=bb5c202c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/012817_d514ad74e4f9519f925b81e27f8dd6d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F012817_d514ad74e4f9519f925b81e27f8dd6d9.jpg&h=5ab5026c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/012818_68badf692a0cfc58206afc2d72baa848.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F012818_68badf692a0cfc58206afc2d72baa848.jpg&h=032dd977&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa2c3a73ad1cecfd0f4f68fb41bb8459e93a8c1a","tid":243553,"uid":25038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:31:10.000Z","msg":"慢慢伸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deaa0e3b549e38d8cd69015ec776c9f21eae3151","tid":243553,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慢慢伸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會嘈醒佢架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c8377d58f517a9ba99b906d523e5dfdc89db06","tid":243553,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:36:26.000Z","msg":"放棄吧"},{"pid":"fa4f7a928334d8f2daf51e342bf458be6ec4513e","tid":243553,"uid":54755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:36:51.000Z","msg":"你瞓個教先，瞓醒隻手就會出返黎"},{"pid":"f76927bf09c975bd38bd620153b8128cb1b6ab45","tid":243553,"uid":42536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:37:30.000Z","msg":"唔洗諗，繼續俾佢瞓，自己坐住瞓又或者睇下電視算"},{"pid":"cbffc8cf7d464b8cecf0ba79a23461a94791c1d8","tid":243553,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:37:51.000Z","msg":"deadpool<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6951505c95589756fae1c5a6bb9cbdfecf8374","tid":243553,"uid":101961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:39:11.000Z","msg":"好cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主不如就咁瞓啦"},{"pid":"aa509e722abd00d23e95bc9b8e0dc